          "reviewBody": "The worst school with trash teachers, trash infrastructure and an arrogant principle in the MUN 3.0 .The delegates were not able to get food. The food suppliers were so bad they were not giving ice cream and the person responsible for giving ice cream was acting to be talking on the phone. DO NOT RECOMMEND TO ANYONE!!!!!",
