            "name": "Shekhar Kulkarni"
          },
          "datePublished": "2024-04-07",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Great school, amazing faculties. Teacher take personal interest in student.\n\nThe child from other state could settle down easily with support from psychology teacher Meghna Bansal. She is always ready to help.\n\nWish to acknowledge Sulochana mam, Kalindi mam, Anushri mam for their excellent teaching.\n\nI wish every success to VBPS.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
            "@type": "School",
            "name": "Vishwa Bharati Public School - Sector 28"
          },
          "author": {
            "@type": "Person",
            "name": "Live Life"
          },
          "datePublished": "2024-03-26",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "1",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "One of the worst schools. Poorly managed by an arrogant principle. Since this principal has come school has just gone down.\n\nThere is no logics been applied. Infra is absolutely zero. Old Aged teachers are doing favour by coming n teaching. If you complain pricipal will target ur ward. Complaints are no welcome. Poor teachers at times look helpless when we complaint,since they themselves are been harassed by the principal and so called vice principals\n\nOne thing is clear either the management is not interested in running the school or the prinicial is not letting the right feedback reach them.\n\nImportant to replace pricincipal & and current set of vice principals. They are of no use. Big fraud is done by the current gang there.\n\nBetter schools in Noida just don't go for this poorly managed school.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
