            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Some teachers are by far the best I have seen in my life especially Namrata Sharma Ma'am and Lissy Abraham Ma'am, they are always polite while talking to the students and even the parents.",
          "publisher": {
