            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "The teacher which i liked the most was our psychology teacher Meghna bansal..I will thank her forever for what she did for me and wanted to say Thankyousomuch ma’am for everything you did for me.. You believed in me and even talked to my mom about me.. That shows how much you care about every child.. Really feeling blessed that i got a teacher like you and thankgod i took psychology… Sorry ma’am if i ever made you sad.. I never wanted that.. I will never forget you in my life at any cost and i will promise that i will stay in contact with you.. You’re the best teacher Ma’am and the only teacher i ever liked hehe.. I am gonna miss your stories ma’am.. Psychology was fun because of you and i took psychology because of you only Ma’am… I love you so so much Ma’am … ❤️i never wrote something like this before to anyone but i think she deserves it fs…\nMa’am this is not buttering or stuffs it’s just how i feel rn\nMa’am you’re the only teacher i am gonna miss and your stories your face your everything🤗 i wish for your good health and take care Ma’am 🥰🤗\nI will miss you so so so much\nAnd i love you ma’am❤️\nI will come to meet you too after my entrance ❤️\nSukriti this side",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
